src:
Henry rocks the runway for Hermes
04 Nov 2019, 20:01 by sl278



Henry was seen in a welcome but unexpected place recently!
The multi-talented musician was seen strutting his stuff for a Hermes runway show in Seoul. Henry was seen walking confidently in a trendy geometric patterned sweater and gray dress pants. 
Check out a video of Henry's walk below!
